Each Sacred Tongue generates 256 tokens using positional bit extraction from a single byte, with tongue-specific phoneme inventories creating distinct phonotactic patterns.

Token generation algorithm:
onset_idx = (byte >> 5) & 0x07   # bits 7-5 -> onset (8 choices)
nucleus_idx = (byte >> 3) & 0x03 # bits 4-3 -> nucleus (4 choices)
coda_idx = byte & 0x07           # bits 2-0 -> coda (8 choices)
token = ONSETS[onset_idx] + NUCLEI[nucleus_idx] + CODAS[coda_idx]

8 x 4 x 8 = 256 tokens per tongue. Bijective by construction — no lookup table needed.

